snippet.title: Fake Deep Thinking
snippet.description:
Fake Deep Thinking is just a group of guys who get together to talk about current events ranging from pop culture, news and politics. Our aim is to promote a platform where everyone feels welcome and comfortable to express their thoughts and ideas no matter where they come from and lead. Through it all we'll do our best to explore thoughts in their entirety within each episode. 

LIVE every Tuesday at 8pm EST! Be sure to tune in on our YouTube channel!
